text: Football Club Sports Réunis Haguenau is a French association football team founded in 1987 as a result of the merger of FC Haguenau 1900 and Sports Réunis Haguenau 1920. They are based in Haguenau, Alsace, France and currently play in the Championnat National 2, the fourth tier in the French football league system.
